pull_request.title: Resizable panels
pull_request.body:
Installs [package/react-resizable-panels](https://www.npmjs.com/package/react-resizable-panels) dependency and plugs it into various parts of Replay.

- [x] Architecture test shell panels
- [x] Console filters / messages
- [ ] Canvas / secondary toolbar split
- [ ] Primary toolbox / Source / secondary toolbox panels

pull_request.title: Try to manually refresh auth state for unauthenticated users
pull_request.body:
I thought the Auth0 SDK would automatically use refresh tokens to refresh access tokens for expired sessions but apparently not.

When `this.update()` is called and the user is not authenticated, try to refresh via `getAccessTokenSilently()`. If it fails, silently redirect to the login page because either the user was logged out or there was some error but the user didn't have an active session so a fresh login will likely fix things.

pull_request.title: Changed code completion type-ahead behavior
pull_request.body:
Update Lexical type-ahead plug-in to more closely mirror Chrome devtools behavior:
1. Don't suggest a code completion after up/down arrow keys
2. Auto dismiss an active suggestion after left/right arrow keys

![Demo of Console auto-complete change](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/29597/210085359-f00fbc13-2422-429f-9c82-6d3d70e65e70.gif)

This change should not impact the _mentions_ plug-in.

cc @Andarist
